   "source": [
    "- 计算输出序列的联合概率 joint probability：\n",
    "    - 先得到从 logprobs 抽取得到按生成顺序排列的记号序列，$\\{t_i,\\ell_i\\}_{i=1}^n, \\quad \\ell_i=\\log p(t_i|t_{\\lt i})$\n",
    "    - $L=\\sum_{i}\\ell_i=\\log\\Pi p$ （先加和）\n",
    "    - $P=\\exp(L)=\\exp(\\log\\Pi p)=\\Pi p(t_i|t_{\\lt i})$（再取 exp）"
   ]
  }
 ],
